install choco by running below commmand in powershell:
powershell -NoProfile -InputFormat None -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -Command "iex ((New-Object System.Net.WebClient).DownloadString('https://chocolatey.org/install.ps1'))"
or
winget install ngrok.ngrok


Cmd for setting auth token: ngrok config add-authtoken <YOUR_AUTHTOKEN>
Cmd to get https: ngrok http 5678


run docker on your https domain:
docker run -d --name n8n -e N8N_HOST="a179-124-123-130-85.ngrok-free.app" -e N8N_PORT=5678 -e N8N_PROTOCOL="http" -e WEBHOOK_URL="https://a179-124-123-130-85.ngrok-free.app/" -e N8N_EDITOR_BASE_URL="https://a179-124-123-130-85.ngrok-free.app/" -p 5678:5678 n8nio/n8n:latest